<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Vansh Saxena | Portfolio</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #8e2de2 0%, #4a00e0 100%);
            color: #333;
            margin: 0;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .portfolio-card {
            background: white;
            max-width: 450px;
            width: 100%;
            border-radius: 25px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
            text-align: center;
            padding-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .header-bg {
            background: #fafafa;
            padding: 40px 20px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
        }

        .profile-img {
            width: 140px;
            height: 140px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            border: 4px solid #4a00e0;
            object-fit: cover;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        h1 {
            margin: 10px 0 5px;
            color: #4a00e0;
            font-size: 26px;
        }

        .tagline {
            color: #888;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            font-size: 13px;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        .info-section {
            padding: 20px 35px;
            text-align: left; /* Easier to read text */
        }

        .bio-text {
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #555;
            font-size: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .details-list {
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }

        .detail-row {
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #444;
        }

        .detail-row strong {
            color: #4a00e0;
        }

        .social-links {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 10px;
        }

        .social-links a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: white;
            background: #4a00e0;
            padding: 10px 18px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: bold;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }

        .social-links a:hover {
            background: #8e2de2;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        .location-footer {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #aaa;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="portfolio-card">
    <div class="header-bg">
        <img src="vansh.jpg" alt="Vansh Saxena" class="profile-img">
        <h1>Vansh Saxena</h1>
        <p class="tagline">B.Tech CSE Student</p>
    </div>

    <div class="info-section">
        <p class="bio-text">
            I am a knowledge gainer and creative person. I am always looking to learn new things and improve my skills. 
            In my free time, I enjoy playing video games and badminton. I also have a keen interest in reading business books.
        </p>

        <div class="details-list">
            <div class="detail-row"><strong>University:</strong> Invertis University, Bareilly</div>
            <div class="detail-row"><strong>Age:</strong> 20 Years</div>
            <div class="detail-row"><strong>From:</strong> Rudrapur, Uttarakhand</div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="social-links">
            <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/vansh-saxena-7101592a6/" target="_blank">LinkedIn</a>
            <a href="https://github.com/Vansh-Saxena-09" target="_blank">GitHub</a>
            <a href="https://www.instagram.com/saxenavansh5" target="_blank">Instagram</a>
        </div>

        <div class="location-footer">
            Built by Vansh • 2026
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>
